sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor H as Human
  participant PL as Planning Lead<br/>parent runtime
  participant II as Ideal Interviewer<br/>human-facing runtime
  participant FSD as Feature Scope Designer<br/>subagent runtime
  participant SD as Spec Designer<br/>subagent runtime
  participant DR as Design Reviewer<br/>subagent runtime
  participant W as Worker<br/>subagent runtime
  participant QA as Code Quality Auditor<br/>subagent runtime
  participant DA as Devil's Advocate<br/>subagent runtime
  participant CA as Compliance Auditor<br/>subagent runtime
  participant CLI as cc-iasd CLI
  participant Src as src/
  participant Art as product/ + ops/ + evidence/

  Note over CLI,Art: Bootstrap / profile update are CLI-scaffolded framework setup, not role-visible runtime.
  CLI-->>Art: initialize project-context scaffold

  H->>PL: governed development request
  activate PL
  PL->>CLI: doctor + view current
  CLI-->>PL: readiness and current context
  Note over PL,DA: Nested subagent runtime is not allowed. Planning Lead launches every specialist subagent.

  alt ideal is missing or too thin
    PL->>II: request ideal interview
    activate II
    II->>H: Communication Packet for ideal clarification
    H-->>II: product intent response
    II->>CLI: ideal add
    CLI-->>Art: product/ideal/iNNN-ideal-id.md + log
    II-->>PL: ideal draft handoff
    PL->>DR: launch ideal design review
    activate DR
    Note over DR: subagent runtime activation
    DR->>CLI: review add for ideal artifact
    CLI-->>Art: evidence review
    DR-->>PL: Design Review Packet
    deactivate DR
    deactivate II
  else ideal is sufficient
    PL->>CLI: continue with existing ideal
    CLI-->>PL: current ideal view
  end

  PL->>FSD: launch feature scope design
  activate FSD
  Note over FSD: subagent runtime activation
  FSD->>CLI: feature add
  CLI-->>Art: feature scope + backlog queue + log
  FSD-->>PL: feature scope handoff
  deactivate FSD
  PL->>DR: launch feature boundary review
  activate DR
  Note over DR: subagent runtime activation
  DR->>CLI: view scope + review add
  CLI-->>Art: feature design review evidence
  DR-->>PL: Design Review Packet
  deactivate DR

  PL->>H: roadmap consultation packet
  H-->>PL: roadmap decision
  PL->>CLI: roadmap add
  CLI-->>Art: roadmap artifact + log

  PL->>SD: launch spec design
  activate SD
  Note over SD: subagent runtime activation
  SD->>CLI: spec add
  CLI-->>Art: spec package + task list + log
  SD-->>PL: spec package handoff
  deactivate SD
  PL->>DR: launch spec review
  activate DR
  Note over DR: subagent runtime activation
  DR->>CLI: view scope + review add
  CLI-->>Art: spec design review evidence
  DR-->>PL: Design Review Packet
  deactivate DR

  PL->>CLI: campaign add
  CLI-->>Art: campaign artifact + log
  PL->>DA: launch Design Launch Review before first run
  activate DA
  Note over DA: subagent runtime activation
  DA->>CLI: view scope + view evidence + review add --review-mode design-launch
  CLI-->>Art: Devil's Advocate design launch evidence
  DA-->>PL: launch findings
  deactivate DA
  alt launch accepted
    PL->>CLI: run start
    CLI-->>Art: run artifacts + logs
  else launch blocked
    PL->>H: escalation or upstream backtrack packet
    H-->>PL: human decision or correction direction
  end

  PL->>W: launch implementation run
  activate W
  Note over W: subagent runtime activation
  W->>CLI: view run
  CLI-->>W: selected tasks and runtime context
  W->>Src: implement selected tasks
  W->>CLI: open-item add when feedback escapes the run
  CLI-->>Art: run-local open item
  W-->>PL: implementation result
  deactivate W
  PL->>QA: launch task-unit code review
  activate QA
  Note over QA: subagent runtime activation
  QA->>CLI: view run + review add
  CLI-->>Art: code quality review evidence
  QA-->>PL: code quality findings
  deactivate QA

  PL->>CLI: view scope + view run
  CLI-->>PL: scoped execution context
  PL->>CLI: open-item resolve when needed
  CLI-->>Art: updated run-local open items

  PL->>DA: launch Campaign Completion Review
  activate DA
  Note over DA: subagent runtime activation
  DA->>CLI: view scope + view run + view evidence + review add --review-mode campaign-completion
  CLI-->>Art: Devil's Advocate review evidence
  DA-->>PL: campaign completion findings
  deactivate DA

  PL->>CA: launch compliance review after Devil's Advocate
  activate CA
  Note over CA: subagent runtime activation
  CA->>CLI: doctor + view evidence + review add
  CLI-->>Art: compliance review evidence
  CA-->>PL: compliance findings
  deactivate CA

  alt completion accepted
    PL->>CLI: campaign mark-run + report
    CLI-->>Art: updated campaign/run state + completion report
    PL->>H: Completion Report Packet
    H-->>PL: confirmation or follow-up direction
  else human decision required
    PL->>CLI: escalate
    CLI-->>Art: escalation packet
    PL->>H: Escalation Packet
    H-->>PL: human decision
  end

  PL->>CLI: log / reference / archive / outdate lifecycle maintenance
  CLI-->>Art: lifecycle maintenance evidence
  deactivate PL
